      </media>
    </figure></problem></exercise>
    <exercise xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" id="fs-id4168594" type="conceptual-questions"><problem id="fs-id1759884">
<para id="import-auto-id1784242">(a) Sketch a graph of velocity versus time corresponding to the graph of position versus time given in <link target-id="import-auto-id2562897"/>. (b) Identify the time or times (<m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mi>t</m:mi><m:mrow><m:mn>a</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msub></m:mrow></m:math>,
<m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mi>t</m:mi><m:mrow><m:mn>b</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msub></m:mrow></m:math>,
